# Constitution (三公理)

## 意图主权

- New repos / large scope → `/plan` or `/scaffold` with AskQuestion（unavailable → numbered prose options; see **master**）；no silent mega-diff.
- `gate-check` must pass before `/run` coding on gated workflows.

## 信号可信

- Claims cite `file:line`; run stated verify commands; no ✅ without `task-verify`.

## 认知可审计

- Decisions in local `plan.md`（gitignore）/ `archive/`; user-visible changes in CHANGELOG.
- Project facts → `/learn` → `.cursorGrowth/learn/` — not `.cursor/`.
